translate jp a3_lilly_diminuendo_1fe70588:

    # "She nods weakly, rubbing my hair with her left hand. If we could simply remain together like this for an eternity, it would be a paradise like no other."
    "リリーは弱々しくうなずいて、左手で俺の髪を撫でる。もし永遠にこんな風にしていられたなら、それに勝る幸福なんてないだろう。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3451
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_cd4f8f87:

    # "After being woken by a sound, I open my eyes with a measure of reluctance."
    "物音で眠りから覚め、俺は嫌々ながら目を開く。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3453
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_fa724298:

    # "Turning my head to the left, I find the rain outside sweeps against the windows loudly. Spray after wind-blown spray lashes against the glass, as if trying its hardest to make up for the summer's previous heat."
    "左に頭を向けると、外では雨が窓に打ち付けられて大きな音を立てている。それまでの夏の暑さを埋め合わせるかのように、風に吹かれたしぶきが次々とガラスにぶつかる。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3455
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_b30fdd9c:

    # "I sit up in the futon, holding the back of my neck to try and subdue the pain from my awkward sleeping position."
    "ふとんの中で体を起こす。変な姿勢で寝ていたおかげで首が痛むのを、手で押さえつけて和らげようとする。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3457
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_2387292a:

    # "By all accounts I should be lamenting the turn in the weather, given that this is our last day here. The events of yesterday refuse to stop flooding my mind, though."
    "今日がここにいられる最後の日なんだし、普通に考えれば俺はこの天気の変化を残念に思うべきところだ。でも昨日の出来事が頭の中でいっぱいになり、離れようとしない。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3459
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_f99a61d6:

    # "The feeling of holding Lilly's crying body in my arms. The rush of lust and hormones that flowed through us as we spent the night together. It seems almost futile to try and rationalize everything that happened."
    "涙に暮れるリリーの体を抱きしめる感触。一夜をともに過ごしたときに、二人の体を埋め尽くした欲情とホルモンの奔流。あのとき起きたことすべてに理屈をつけるのはまず無駄なことだろう。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3461
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_1d7cc4ac:

    # "In an attempt to distract myself, I groan and lean over to retrieve my bag without standing. Pulling out one bottle after another, I take the daily regimen's worth of pills from their containers and swallow them without further ado."
    "気分を変えようとして、うめきながら体を伸ばして、立ち上がらずにかばんを引き寄せる。次々に薬びんを取り出して、処方された一日分の薬を手に取ると、苦もなく飲み下す。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3467
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_87d6877d:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=120}It took a surprisingly short amount of time to get used to swallowing pills without water. That said, I suppose the same thing goes for getting used to living in a school for disabled students."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\n\n水なしで薬を飲むことには驚くほど早いうちに慣れた。とはいえ、障害児のための学校で暮らすことにも同じように慣れたと言えるだろう。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3471
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_d30e5e67:

    # n "Remembering Yamaku, I become all the more grateful for having the chance to get away, even if it's just for the shortest of times."
    n "山久のことを思い出して、そこから離れる機会が得られたことに一層感謝の念が強まる。それがほんのわずかな間だとしても。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3473
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_14d37258:

    # n "I appreciate the chance to spend time alone with Lilly and Hanako, away from the bustle of school life, even considering the latest complications."
    n "このところトラブルがあったとはいえ、せわしない学校生活を離れて、リリーや華子と一緒に過ごせることをありがたく思う。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3475
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_60cef8ec:

    # n "I never thought I'd say it, but the idea of living away from the city in a nice, tranquil area is an inviting one. It's a thought that, barely a year ago, would have seemed simply ludicrous."
    n "こんな気持ちになるとは思わなかったけど、街から離れて静かなところで暮らすというのも悪くないな。たった１年前なら、ばかばかしいとしか思えなかっただろう。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3479
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3482
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_bbcb44a1:

    # "A flash of pink, no doubt Hanako's gown, peeks from around the corner. Realizing I must look a sight since I've only just woken up, I slap the remaining pills into my mouth and run a hand through my hair."
    "角の向こうで、ピンク色がちらりと目に入る。華子のガウンだ。たぶん起きたばかりでひどい格好になっているだろうと気づいて、残りの薬を口に放り込み、手櫛で髪をなでつける。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3487
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_06e1a86e:

    # ha "Good morning, Hisao."
    ha "おはよう、久夫くん"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3489
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_39e03557:

    # hi "Ah, go— ack!"
    hi "ああ、おは――げほっ！"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3495
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_55b59283:

    # "I reply to her completely forgetting that I'm in the middle of swallowing a particularly large pill. Coughing and spluttering, I violently gag on it."
    "とびきり大きい錠剤を飲み込んでいることを完全に忘れて返事をしてしまう。薬が思い切りのどに詰まって汚らしく咳き込む。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3500
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_dba8bb47:

    # ha "Ah, Hisao!"
    ha "あっ、久夫くん！"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3504
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_fba4dfb9:

    # "After sputtering loudly and tapping my chest a couple of times to force it down, I manage to recover."
    "大きな音を立ててむせ返り、何度か胸を叩いて強引に飲み下して、どうにか立ち直る。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3506
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_28a794da:

    # hi "I'm fine. Sorry, forgot I was swallowing."
    hi "大丈夫。ごめん、薬を飲もうとしてたの忘れてた"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3513
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_f238fc1d:

    # ha "Sorry, I didn't mean to—"
    ha "ごめんね、邪魔するつもりじゃ――"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3515
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_df4351f6:

    # "I hold my hand up, gesturing for Hanako to stop."
    "俺は手を上げて、華子をとどめる。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3517
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_055c2588:

    # hi "I gagged. It's my fault. 'Morning, Hanako."
    hi "むせたのは俺だから。華子は悪くないよ。おはよう、華子"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3519
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_5c514a35:

    # "She pauses a moment before bowing in reply."
    "ちょっとためらってから、華子はおじぎを返す。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3528
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_77137d31:

    # "Walking, no, staggering in behind Hanako is the familiar figure of Lilly, also dressed in her pajamas. With her eyes full of sleep and hair bedraggled, she's a sight to behold."
    "華子の後ろからこちらに歩いて、いや、よろめいてくるのは見慣れたリリーの姿だ。こちらもパジャマを着ている。とても眠そうな目つきとくしゃくしゃの髪の毛のおかげで、とんだ見物になっている。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3530
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_4d5294c9:

    # hi "Hi, Lilly."
    hi "よう、リリー"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3535
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_9f705762:

    # li "Good morning… Hisao."
    li "おはようございます……久夫さん"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3537
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_efe1376b:

    # "For a while, a silence hangs in the air as neither of us knows what to do."
    "しばらくの間、お互い何をしていいのか分からないかのように、空気に沈黙がただよう。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3539
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_b6b07126:

    # "Given what happened last night, we both have more than enough reason to be finding the situation awkward; just how are we meant to react to meeting each other after something like… that?"
    "昨日の出来事を考えれば、二人ともこの状況を気まずいと思う理由には事欠かない。あんなことがあった後で……いったいどんな反応をすればいいんだ？"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3541
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_d9f6caa3:

    # "The best course of action would probably be to talk to Lilly alone, to set things in order."
    "たぶん一番いいのは、リリーと二人きりで話して、きちんと解決することだ。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3543
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_6ea509bf:

    # hi "Um, I'll… start making breakfast."
    hi "あの、俺……朝ご飯作るから"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3545
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_b651cf83:

    # "Lilly evidently catches on to my train of thought."
    "リリーがどうやら俺の考えに気づく。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3550
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_1b5da563:

    # li "I'll help. Hanako, could you set the table?"
    li "手伝います。華ちゃん、テーブルに食器を並べてくれる？"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3552
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_3df55ec5:

    # "She nods, her head disappearing into a cupboard as she quickly goes about her assigned task."
    "華子はうなずくとすぐに手伝いに取りかかり、その頭が食器棚に隠れる。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3559
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_81421c17:

    # "I rub a little more sleep out of my eyes as I wander over to the fridge and take out some milk, and Lilly grabs various brightly colored boxes from some of the lower cupboards to my side."
    "俺は眠い目をこすって冷蔵庫の方へと歩き、ミルクを取り出す。リリーは俺の足下の横にある戸棚から、様々な明るい色の箱を出してくる。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3561
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_39a4d067:

    # "While we make the rather bland-looking meal, I whisper somewhat more quietly than usual. Knowing Lilly's hearing, she won't have any trouble catching what I say."
    "どちらかと言えば淡泊な食事を用意する間、俺は普段よりも小さな声でひそひそと話す。リリーの耳の良さは知っているから、問題なく聞き取れるだろう。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3563
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_f5015ab4:

    # hi "Are you okay, Lilly? After last night…"
    hi "大丈夫か、リリー？　あの後で……"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3568
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_04cd878d:

    # "She gives a delicate nod, her expression weak."
    "リリーはかすかにうなずく。その表情には力がない。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3570
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_18b019b4:

    # "Though her tiredness surely plays a part, she seems genuinely unsure about what's happened between us, and how to move ahead. I can't say I blame her, considering my feelings are the same."
    "もちろん疲れているせいもあるだろうけど、純粋に俺たちの間に起きた出来事のこと、これからどうしていけばいいのかということを不安に思っているみたいだ。無理もない。俺だって同じ気持ちだから。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3575
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_0ebe277e:

    # li "I'm sorry, Hisao. I wasn't thinking straight yesterday. I never stopped to consider you or Hanako, and I even went as far as…"
    li "ごめんなさい、久夫さん。昨日の私はどうかしていました。あなたや華ちゃんのことを気遣いもしなくて、しかもあんなことまで……"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3577
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_f4a6a6bc:

    # "She's winding herself up. With her hands and voice both tightening, I give her a gentle bump to try and lighten up the situation."
    "リリーは動転している。その手も声もこわばり始めていたので、俺はそっと体を当てて場を和らげてみる。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3579
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_c7c8d84b:

    # hi "You don't have to apologize. I said I liked you as well, after all."
    hi "謝ることなんてないよ。第一、俺もリリーのことは好きだって言っただろ"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3584
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_87c34db5:

    # li "But I…"
    li "でも、私……"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3586
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_43f525a3:

    # "As her composure begins to falter, it becomes obvious there's no alternative."
    "リリーが落ち着きをなくしていく。俺にできることは一つしかない。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3591
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_b2ac5235:

    # "Turning to Lilly, I gently embrace her tall frame. She offers no resistance at all, thankfully pulling back, just, from the edge of her emotions."
    "リリーに向かい合い、その背の高い体をそっとかき抱く。リリーはまったく逆らわず、幸いにもぎりぎりのところで、平静を取り戻す。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3600
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_c931375e:

    # "Despite our reassuring embrace lasting only a matter of seconds, I notice Hanako wordlessly watching. The plate in her hand hovers inches above the table, her action halted midway by the sight."
    "心休まる抱擁はすぐに終わりにしたのだけど、華子が言葉もなくこちらを見ていることに気づいてしまう。その手に持ったお皿はテーブルの数センチ上で浮いていて、俺たちを見つめたまま動きが止まっている。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3615
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_0390c97b:

    # "The clatter of utensils against plates is the only sound to be heard as we silently eat. Whereas before only two of us may have been unsure of ourselves, the entire situation has changed."
    "無言で食事をする間、食器と皿のこすれ合う音だけが聞こえる。これまでは俺たち二人だけが自分たちのことに不安を抱いていたのかもしれない。でも今は状況が完全に変わってしまった。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3617
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_6f239bcf:

    # "After weeks of blissful friendship, whiling away the days with shared meals and chatter with little meaning, the relationship of Lilly and me, no, that of all of us, has irreversibly changed."
    "一緒の食事と他愛もない会話で時間を費やしながら、数週間の幸福な友情を経て、リリーと俺の関係――いや、俺たち全員の関係は後戻りができないまでに変わってしまった。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3619
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_f19b02b0:

    # "I can't take this."
    "こんなのは耐えられない。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3621
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_5e04a1b9:

    # hi "Lilly…"
    hi "リリー……"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3628
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_08e54d8d:

    # "She solemnly nods, gently laying her spoon onto the plate in front of her. Neither of us knows exactly how we regard each other, let alone how Hanako would view us."
    "リリーは厳かにうなずき、目の前の皿にそっとスプーンを置く。お互いのことをどう思っているのか、俺たちのどちらもはっきりとはわかっていない。華子がどう思っているかはなおのことだ。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3633
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_f855f278:

    # li "This might seem abrupt but… I've confessed to Hisao."
    li "突然と思うかもしれないけど……私、久夫さんに告白したの"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3638
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_8e99f27f:

    # "For a moment, Hanako looks almost confused; precisely the reaction I'd thought she would have. She eventually nods, her spoon still in her mouth as she does."
    "一瞬、華子は困惑したかのように見えた。俺の予想していたとおりの反応だ。やがてスプーンを口の中に入れたまま、華子はうなずく。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3643
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_ee42563e:

    # ha "Did you accept?"
    ha "受け入れたの？"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3645
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_61becb50:

    # hi "I did."
    hi "ああ"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3650
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_b78f72d2:

    # "She gives a smile so large, and so earnest, I find myself blushing. I think it's the brightest I've ever seen her expression look."
    "華子はとびきりの、心からの笑顔を見せる。自分の顔が赤くなるのがわかる。こんなに明るい華子の表情は初めてだと思う。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3654
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_f975527a:

    # ha "Then I'm happy. I'm really, really happy."
    ha "なら、よかった。ほんとに、ほんとによかった"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3659
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_5888dca1:

    # li "I'm sorry for not telling you anything about it before. Things have been…"
    li "今まで何も言わなくてごめんなさい。いろいろなことがあって……"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3661
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_05eb7eb8:

    # "Hanako shakes her head from side to side emphatically, apparently forgetting in her rush that Lilly couldn't possibly notice."
    "華子は力強く首を左右に振る。急いでいてリリーには分かりようがないことも忘れているのだろう。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3666
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_61787ea8:

    # "She begins fiddling with her fingers, looking a little more nervous than she did before."
    "すると、それまでよりも少しそわそわとした様子で、自分の指をもてあそぶ。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3668
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_ca048762:

    # ha "To be honest, I began to think you might like each other a while ago. At first I didn't really know what to think about it… but I…"
    ha "ほんとのことを言うと、ちょっと前から二人はお互いのことが好きなんじゃないかな、って思い始めてたの。最初はなんて考えればいいのか分からなかったけど……でも……"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3673
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_6203cc6e:

    # ha "I decided in the end that… if my friends are happy, then I'm happy."
    ha "私、思ったの……友達が幸せなら、自分も幸せだって"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3675
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_83107b8d:

    # ha "I was really glad to have another friend when we met Hisao, so you finding love through him is even better… right?"
    ha "久夫くんに出会ったとき、友達が増えることがすごくうれしかった。だからリリーが久夫くんと恋人同士になるのって、もっと素敵だと思う……そうでしょ？"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3677
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_c3189320:

    # "A feeling of relief at her acceptance of our relationship falls over me like a wave. The same happens to Lilly, judging by her expression."
    "華子が俺たちの関係を認めてくれたという安堵の気持ちが、波のように押し寄せてくる。リリーもその表情からすると、同じ気持ちみたいだ。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3682
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_b07e36e4:

    # li "Thank you, Hanako. I really appreciate you being so understanding."
    li "ありがとう、華ちゃん。分かってくれて、本当にうれしいわ"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3687
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_1a73e217:

    # "Lilly's voice still sounds slightly apologetic, or at least unsure. This doesn't escape Hanako, who appears lost in thought for a few moments before turning to me."
    "リリーの声にはまだ申し訳なさそうな、少なくとも不安そうな響きが残っている。華子はそれを聞き逃さない。しばらく考え込んだ後、俺に向き直る。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3692
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_a983f1ce:

    # ha "Hisao, do you mind if Lilly and I go outside for a bit?"
    ha "久夫くん、ちょっとリリーと外に行ってもいい？"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3694
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_22aca4a2:

    # hi "Ah, no, feel free…"
    hi "ああ、うん、どうぞ……"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3699
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_dc6591cc:

    # li "Hanako?"
    li "華ちゃん？"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3714
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_f0bf2400:

    # "Hanako gets up from her seat, taking Lilly's hand and almost dragging her from the table in her excitement. Considering Lilly's typically slow and steady pace, Hanako's haste makes her footing awkward and she almost loses her balance a couple of times."
    "華子は席を立ってリリーの手を取り、興奮のあまりほとんど引きずるように導いていく。普段のリリーの歩みは緩やかで規則的なので、華子が急ぐおかげでぎこちなくなってしまい、何度かよろけそうになる。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3716
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_a3e4e8b3:

    # "It's a pretty amusing sight, leaving me wordless as I watch them disappear out the door. It's only now that I realize the rain's stopped, being replaced by a sky seemingly all the more vivid and bright to make up for the morning's drab gray expanse."
    "かなり愉快な光景だ。二人がドアの外へ姿を消すのを、俺は言葉もなく眺める。今になって気づいたけど、雨はもう上がっていて、朝方のくすんだ灰色の空は、ずっと鮮やかでまぶしい色彩に移り変わっていた。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3718
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_16185b69:

    # "For Hanako, this must be a pretty big revelation. Lilly and I are really the only people she associates with, almost as if we were parents in her own's stead."
    "華子にとってはかなり重大な知らせに違いない。実際、彼女とつきあいのある人間はリリーと俺だけだ。まるで本来の肉親の代わりに、俺たちが華子の両親であるかのように。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3720
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_ab0ee8fe:

    # "I suppose that might well be the best way to describe the relationship we share. A father, mother and daughter, all playing around in our little make-believe family as if it could last forever."
    "もしかしたら、それが俺たちが分かち合っているこの関係を一番良く言い表しているのかもしれない。父親、母親、そして娘。みんながこの小さな見せかけの家族を、永遠に続くもののように演じ続けている。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3722
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_c65e3000:

    # "It might be a strange dynamic, and one that certainly can't last for long… but maybe, just for this one small moment, it's okay."
    "おかしな関係かもしれないし、間違いなく長続きはしない……でも、このひとときだけなら、いいんじゃないだろうか。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3724
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_89bb3162:

    # "As I stand from the table and go to join Lilly and Hanako in the fields outside, I nod to myself in affirmation."
    "外にいるリリーと華子に加わろうと、俺は食卓から立つ。そして確認するように、自分に向かってうなずく。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3726
translate jp a3_lilly_gray_outlook_44dd00a5:

    # "This one small moment of happiness, no matter how brief, will last with me, with all of us, forever."
    "この小さな幸福の時間は、どんなに短くたって、俺の心に、みんなの心に、永遠に残るだろう。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3738
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_f5f687cb:

    # "Submerged deep in the hot water, I let a drawn-out sigh escape my lips. The feeling of seemingly every muscle in my body relaxing is euphoric."
    "お湯に深く浸かって、俺は長々とため息を漏らす。体中の筋肉がリラックスする感覚がたまらない。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3740
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_25d6306b:

    # "I have no idea how long it's been since I had a genuine hot bath, but right now I can hardly be bothered trying to remember."
    "ゆっくり風呂に入ったのはどれだけ久しぶりだろう。でも今わざわざ思い出す気にはとてもなれない。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3744
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3747
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_81de881d:

    # n "Maybe I'm giving the simple fact that for once I get to have a real bath more credit than it's due; the chance to just calm down, allow myself to unwind and have some time to myself is a welcome one."
    n "たまの機会に本物の風呂に入るという単純な出来事を、必要以上に評価しすぎているのかもしれない。ただ落ち着いて、緊張を解いて、自分だけの時間を過ごすというのはありがたいことだ。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3749
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_70632b1b:

    # n "Hanako, Lilly and I wandered about outside, exploring the extent of the surprisingly large tract of land surrounding the house. Then we spent the majority of the afternoon resting, watching television, reading, and playing cards."
    n "華子とリリーと俺は外をぶらつき、家の周りの驚くほど広大な土地を散策した。午後の残りの時間はほとんど、テレビや読書やトランプなどでゆっくりと過ごした。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3751
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_269ef718:

    # n "It may not have been the most exciting finale to the trip, but such tranquil peacefulness is something to savor. Even after we return to the school tomorrow, I think I'll remember this little house in Hokkaido for a long time."
    n "旅行の最後のひとときにしては盛り上がりに欠けるけど、こういう穏やかさはじっくり満喫するべきものだ。明日学校に戻った後でも、この北海道の小さな家のことはずっと忘れないだろう。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3753
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_19baac3a:

    # n "It's a pity we only have a couple more hours to spend here before going to get the train back."
    n "帰りの電車に乗るまで、あと数時間しかここにいられないのが残念だ。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3755
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_fa347bf4:

    # n "All I can do is yawn contentedly while I watch the steam slowly rising from the clear water's placid surface, my eyes eventually locking onto the ceiling."
    n "俺にできるのは、満足げにあくびをしながら、穏やかな水面から立ち上る湯気を眺めることだけだ。やがて俺の目は天井を見つめる。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3757
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_68f552e1:

    # n "Our exams are imminent. I've barely studied at all for them."
    n "もうすぐ試験だ。どの科目もほとんど勉強していない。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3759
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_0dbd0fef:

    # n "On top of that, I don't even know what I'll do after graduation. Passing exams is all well and good, but to what end?"
    n "しかも、卒業後の進路をどうするか、まるで考えていない。試験に合格するのはいいとして、目的はどうなんだ？"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3761
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_3553b764:

    # n "Also now, of all times, I'm getting into a relationship."
    n "それに今は、よりにもよって恋愛関係まで持ち始めている。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3763
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3766
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_0d768b95:

    # hi "What the hell am I doing?"
    hi "いったい何やってるんだよ、俺は？"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3768
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3770
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_98e4d7a6:

    # "…I guess I shouldn't think like that. What's done is done, and maybe this could be viewed as just another aspect of my new life that I'm working on."
    "……そんな考え方はしちゃだめだな。済んだことは仕方がない。これだって、俺が今体験している新しい人生の一つの側面でしかない、とも言える。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3772
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_4f9eb757:

    # "I enjoy being with Lilly, and there's more to life than school and a career after all."
    "リリーといるのは楽しいし、学校と仕事が人生の全てってわけじゃない。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3774
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_a1e74857:

    # "As I busily attempt to rationalize all that's happened, I hear a series of raps on the door. I pick myself up and sit upright, trying to figure out the source."
    "そうやってせっせと自己弁護をしていると、何度かドアを叩く音が聞こえてくる。俺は体を起こしてまっすぐ座り、それが誰なのかを探ろうとする。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3776
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_6e158e4f:

    # "Three, no more and no less. Light yet assertive in their tapping, and timed regularly enough to tune a metronome. I'd be extremely surprised if it wasn't Lilly."
    "３回、それ以上でも以下でもない。軽くだけどはっきりとしたノック。メトロノームだって調律できそうな規則的なタイミング。これがリリーじゃなければびっくりするだろう。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3778
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_b9f1162f:

    # li "May I… come in?"
    li "入っても……いいですか？"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3780
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_f9ca4997:

    # "Yeah, it's Lilly."
    "ああ、やっぱりリリーだ。"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3782
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_3af69fef:

    # hi "I'm still in the bath, I'll be out in a sec."
    hi "まだ入ってるんだ、すぐ出るよ"

# game/script-a3-lilly.rpy:3784
translate jp a3_lilly_rhapsody_in_blue_9b367cb2:

